Measures systolic and diastolic blood pressure and heart rate;
8.7" - 16.5" cuff circumference;
90-memory storage;
LCD display;
Includes AA batteries.
Tracks: Systolic Diastolic Pulse Atrial Fibrillation Tachycardia Bradycardia
